    //Asz          - Shear area in the local z-axis of a prismatic frame element in^2  or mm^2
    //Aply         - Plastic shear area for shear acting parallel to the y-axis in^2  or mm^2 //not set in .3dd file
    //Aplz         - Plastic shear area for shear acting parallel to the z-axis in^2  or mm^2 //not set in .3dd file
    //Iy           - Moment of inertia for bending about the local y axis  in^4 or  mm^4
    //Iz           - Moment of inertia for bending about the local z axis  in^4 or  mm^4
    //Jx           - Torsional moment of inertia of a frame element  in^4 or  mm^4 replaced by It
